Database transfer agent

In this point we need agent that will transfer values from old Logbook file (excel)
to our new database
This have to be separate app

General working principle:

user open Transfer Agent

user select present database file
user select source file
user have to be sure that source file is correct becouse agent will always copy data in the same way from same columns.

agent have to temove all database inputs without seed input
seed is important for user for correction.
becouse old loogbok have data from many years user have to chose time distance that he want to transfer.
FROM ..... TO ......
AGent must transfer values to new database in the same order. 

Some old entries can be missing according Input card in New Loogbok. Like MID parameters, Scrubber RT or Diesel Generators power produced. Thats fine. New program must accept this. Old values transfered must not be able to be changed by user.

In old excel loogbok values are created mostly by formulas. Agent should first read calculated value in cell then copy value. Not the formula.

